name: "I can't explain"
description:
There are incidents and moments in life that make us feel things that cannot be expressed using mankind's limited vocabulary.
Moments filled with raw feelings and emotions that touch our souls but are not easy to be manifested into the lingual bricks we call words.
Perhaps one day, we will discover new words to release the inexplicable feelings within us but until then, art is our only hope for expressing ourselves when language fails.
It is a painting by me that was completed in January 2021.

Size: 7650px by 9900px
